<% content_for :title, "Furniture Financing – Lease-to-Own with Acima | Warehouse Furniture Killeen TX" %>
<% content_for :description, "Shop now, pay over time. Warehouse Furniture offers lease-to-own financing through Acima Leasing — no credit check required. Apply in minutes at our Killeen, TX store." %>

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">

  <%# ── Hero ── %>
  <div class="text-center mb-14">
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-warm-500 mb-3">Flexible Payments</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-warm-950 mb-4">Furniture Financing Available</h1>
    <p class="text-warm-600 text-base max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      We've partnered with <strong class="text-warm-800">Acima Leasing</strong> so you can take your furniture home today
      and pay over time, with no credit check required.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start mb-14">

    <%# ── Left: What is Acima + How it Works ── %>
    <div class="space-y-8">

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-warm-300 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-warm-950 mb-4">What is Acima Leasing?</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-warm-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Acima is a <strong class="text-warm-900">lease-to-own</strong> program, not a loan. Acima purchases the
          furniture on your behalf and leases it to you with flexible payment options. Once all payments are
          complete, you own it. You can also use the <strong class="text-warm-900">90-day early purchase option</strong>
          to pay off the lease amount plus a $10 fee and own your furniture right away.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-warm-700 leading-relaxed">
          Acima uses <strong class="text-warm-900">no traditional credit check</strong>, only a soft pull that
          won't affect your credit score. Approval is based on income and bank account history, making it a
          great option for customers with less-than-perfect or limited credit.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-warm-300 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-warm-950 mb-5">How It Works</h2>
        <ol class="space-y-5">
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-warm-800 text-warm-50 text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">1</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-warm-900">Apply in minutes</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-warm-600 mt-0.5">Scan the QR code or click the button to start your application. You'll enter your income and bank account information. Most decisions are instant.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-warm-800 text-warm-50 text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">2</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-warm-900">Get approved for a lease amount</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-warm-600 mt-0.5">Acima approves you for a lease between $300–$5,000. Bring your approval to our store and pick your furniture.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-warm-800 text-warm-50 text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">3</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-warm-900">Take it home today</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-warm-600 mt-0.5">Choose a payment schedule that matches your paycheck: weekly, bi-weekly, twice-monthly, or monthly. Payments are automatic from your checking account.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-warm-800 text-warm-50 text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">4</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-warm-900">Own it your way</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-warm-600 mt-0.5">Pay off the lease within 90 days (lease amount + $10 fee) and save the most. Or complete a 12, 18, or 24-month lease term and own it at the end. You can also cancel the lease at any time with no penalty.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

    </div>

    <%# ── Right: QR + CTA ── %>
    <div class="space-y-6">

      <%# QR card %>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-warm-300 p-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-warm-500 mb-1">Scan to Apply</p>
        <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-warm-950 mb-6">Point your phone camera at the code below</h2>

        <% if @qr_svg.present? %>
          <div class="w-52 h-52 mx-auto mb-6 p-3 border border-warm-200 rounded-xl bg-warm-50">
            <%== @qr_svg %>
          </div>
        <% end %>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 my-5">
          <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-warm-200"></div>
          <span class="text-xs text-warm-400 font-medium">or</span>
          <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-warm-200"></div>
        </div>

        <% if @acima_url.present? %>
          <%= link_to @acima_url,
              target: "_blank", rel: "noopener noreferrer",
              class: "block w-full bg-warm-800 hover:bg-warm-700 text-warm-50 font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-full transition-colors text-sm" do %>
            Apply Now at Acima &rarr;
          <% end %>
        <% end %>

        <p class="text-xs text-warm-400 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Opens the Acima Leasing application in a new tab.<br>
          Applications typically take 2–3 minutes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <%# Qualification requirements %>
      <div class="bg-warm-50 rounded-2xl border border-warm-300 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-warm-900 mb-3">Do I qualify?</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-warm-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
            Active checking account open for at least 90 days
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
            Regular income of at least $750/month
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
            Government-issued photo ID
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
            SSN or Taxpayer ID Number
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
            Must be 18 years or older
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
            </svg>
            No traditional credit check (soft pull only)
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-warm-500 mt-4 leading-relaxed">
          Approval is not guaranteed and is subject to Acima's criteria. Lease-to-own agreements involve a total cost higher than the retail price if carried to full term. See Acima's website for complete terms, state-specific details, and early purchase option calculations.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <%# ── Bottom CTA ── %>
  <div class="bg-warm-50 border border-warm-300 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-warm-950 mb-2">Ready to furnish your home?</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-warm-600 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-6">
      Browse our full selection and apply for Acima financing when you're ready, or stop by our Killeen showroom and we'll walk you through it in person.
    </p>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
      <%= link_to "Shop All Furniture", products_path,
          class: "bg-warm-800 text-warm-50 px-7 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-warm-700 transition-colors" %>
      <%= link_to "Contact Us", contact_path,
          class: "text-warm-700 text-sm font-medium underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-warm-950 transition-colors" %>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
